A gravimetric feature almost parallel and near the Paran River indicates the presence of an anomalous deep body.
We have presented a 2-D geoelectric model of the deep structure in the Paran Basin.
Presence of a high conductivity band in the upper part, that represents the sedimentary basin.
High resistivity body below the area of the basin.
Our model may help to understand the geological structure of the Paran Basin.
